00:20:39,219 --> 00:20:53,190
Medford Vocational Technical High School is seeking school committee approval to submit a statement of interest to the Massachusetts Building Association for the renovation of existing space and the increase of lab space for the STEM-related fields.

291
00:20:54,511 --> 00:21:02,638
Medford Public Schools opened the vocational school in 1970 after a major build that included the high school being on the same complex.

292
00:21:03,867 --> 00:21:08,748
