294
00:21:17,970 --> 00:21:28,172
MVTHS intends to implement a strategic plan that would reorganize the vocational campus to embrace the need to move programs in cluster or academy type models.

295
00:21:29,915 --> 00:21:32,196
The following are the potential academies.

296
00:21:33,237 --> 00:21:40,161
The Construction Academy would house carpentry, construction and craft labors, electrical, and HVAC.

297
00:21:41,622 --> 00:21:56,130
The Design and Visual Academy would include graphic communications, design and visual communications, media technology, which is also often known as TV production, computer programming, and web development.

298
00:21:58,012 --> 00:22:03,253
In the Human Services Academy, it would house Health Assisting, Early Education and Childhood.

299
00:22:04,514 --> 00:22:12,535
In the Service Academy, it would house Business Technology, Cosmetology, Culinary Arts, Hospitality and Marketing.

300
00:22:13,816 --> 00:22:23,498
And the STEM Academy would include Biotechnology, Environmental Science, Robotics, Engineering, Metal Fabrication and Advanced Manufacturing.

301
00:22:25,595 --> 00:22:43,821
MVTHS is planning to seek funding under priority number seven of the MSBA priorities, which states replacement of or addition to obsolete buildings in order to provide a full range of programs consistent with state and approved local requirements.

302
00:22:44,521 --> 00:22:47,882
